OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FMinister quit as he        
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'couldn't afford mortgage' 
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, A Tory MP said he quit his ministerial 
OL,6, role because he could not afford to pay
OL,7, his mortgage on a salary of #118,300.  
OL,9,FMid Norfolk MP George Freeman resigned 
OL,10,Fas science minister in November.       
OL,12,FIn a blog post, he said he stood down: 
OL,13,F"Because my mortgage rises this month  
OL,14,Ffrom #800pcm to #2,000, which I simply 
OL,15,Fcouldn't afford to pay on a ministerial
OL,16,Fsalary."                               
OL,18,FDowning Street said it had "no plans to
OL,19,Fchange our approach to ministerial     
OL,20,Fpay".                                  
